<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-06-11T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-06-11T18:00:00-05:00" n="581" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d581">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00115 EW/6–1145: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Armour</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-06-11T19:00:00-04:00">June 11,
                                    1945—7 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>991. To extent situation warrants it and your Brit colleague supports
                            you, you should request local authorities place under house arrest or
                            stricter measures of control where applicable all German officials and
                            agents designated by you stating US and Brit Govts making every effort
                            expedite prompt repatriation these categories.</p>
                        <p>Report results.</p>
                        <p>Repeated to Lisbon, Dublin, Bern, Stockholm and Tangier.<note n="8" xml:id="d581fn8">Repeated to Lisbon as 981, to Dublin as 102, to
                                Bern as 2015, to Stockholm as 1102, and to Tangier as 123.</note>
                        </p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>